  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The delicious daily buffet breakfast includes a range of hot and cold items.</p>
<p>In the evening, enjoy a delicious four-course meal that is either served or a buffet, as part of the Half Board package.</p>
<p>The hotel also has the à la carte <strong>Julijana Restaurant </strong>(open on the weekends only) and the <strong>Park Café, </strong>which serves à la carte meals, snacks and delicious cakes.</p>
<p>If you're booked on Half Board but would like to eat in the Park Café or Julijana Restaurant you can request this locally. You'll receive a €15 voucher per person in lieu of the Half Board meal.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
