  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Private Lakeside lido (open from mid-June to mid-Sept) with direct access to the lake, deckchairs and umbrellas</li>
<li>Indoor pool (not heated) filled with water from the thermal springs - water temp approx. 22C</li>
<li>Spa Luisa has Finnish, Turkish and infrared saunas and private terrace with lake views</li>
<li>Massage and beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Rowing boats available to hire (payable locally - one hour free rental included once per stay)</li>
<li>Parking</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots &amp; linen available (approx. €10 per cot, per stay - payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
