  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms</strong> are around 22-25m² and sleep two people. These rooms have Austrian Twin beds (not separable) and area available for sole occupancy for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms with Lake View</strong> are available for a supplement. These are also available for sole occupancy for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Suites</strong> are around 39-45m² have a balcony with lake view, Austrian Twin beds (not separable), and a bath. They can sleep two to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed) and are available on request - please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 13-15m² and have a balcony and a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Ensuite with bath or shower</li>
<li>Air Conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea/coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>2pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €3.13 per adult per night is payable locally. Children aged 7-17 years pay a discounted rate of approx. €1.57 per night, and children aged 6 and under are exempt. A registration fee of €2.50 per person per stay incl. children from 2 years is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
